COMPANY FAQ

Refund Policy:
Customers can request a full refund within 30 days of purchase.
Refund requests submitted after 30 days are not eligible.
Refunds are processed within 5-7 business days.

Subscription Cancellation:
Customers can cancel their subscription at any time from their account settings.
Cancellation stops future billing but does not automatically issue a refund.

Payment Methods:
We accept Visa, Mastercard, American Express, UPI, and PayPal.

Shipping:
We offer international shipping to most countries.
Shipping charges are calculated during checkout.

Delivery Time:
Domestic orders are usually delivered within 3-5 business days.
International orders are usually delivered within 7-14 business days.

Order Tracking:
Customers receive a tracking link by email after the order has been shipped.

Account Access:
If a customer forgets their password, they can use the "Forgot Password" option on the login page.

Support Hours:
Customer support is available Monday to Friday from 9:00 AM to 6:00 PM IST.

Contact Information:
For general support, customers can email support@company.com.

Product Warranty:
All products include a standard 1-year warranty against manufacturing defects.

Exchanges:
Products can be exchanged within 15 days of delivery if they are unused and in their original condition.

Business Plans:
Enterprise and custom plans are available for businesses with more than 100 users.

Security:
Customer data is encrypted and stored securely according to industry standards.